author: Doreen Christensen
title: $20 off one-year membership at BJ's Wholesale Club
text:
$20 off one-year membership at BJ's Wholesale Club Shop are BJ's Wholesale Club for two months for free. 
BJ's Wholesale Club is offering $20 off a new membership. 
Sign up online only for a one-year membership for $30. A yearly Inner Circle membership costs $50. 
BJ's, which has the cheapest gas in town, offers its own coupons and accepts manufacturer coupons, (Sam's Club and Costco don't) so you can save even more. 
Not sure you want to go all-in? New members can get a free 60-day trial membership with full benefits and pay no surcharge at checkout. 
Click here for the deals. The offers ends on Oct. 23.
